'''生活的藝術基金會'''(Art of Living foundation，縮寫'''AOLF''')乃是基於義工服務、[[人道主義|人道]]及教育精神的NGO[[非政府組織|非政府組織]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=生活的藝術基金會|url=http://www.guidestar.org/organizations/77-0240101/art-living-foundation.aspx|publisher=GuideStar USA, Inc|accessdate=20 September 2013|archive-date=2013-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130518102122/http://www.guidestar.org/organizations/77-0240101/art-living-foundation.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>由[[詩麗詩麗·若威香卡|詩麗詩麗·若威香卡]]（暱稱「[[古儒吉大師|古儒吉大師]]」）成立於1981年。<ref>{{cite news|title=沒有一門生意堪比神的事業：印度神人發現靈性可以是有利可圖的|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/lifestyle/1888934/report-no-business-like-god-business-india-s-godmen-find-spirituality-to-be-profitable|accessdate=20 September 2013|newspaper=DNA|date=15 Sep 2013|archive-date=2013-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921053855/http://www.dnaindia.com/lifestyle/1888934/report-no-business-like-god-business-india-s-godmen-find-spirituality-to-be-profitable|dead-url=no}}</ref>

該基金會亦為[[聯合國經濟及社會理事會|聯合國經濟及社會理事會]]（縮寫UN's ECOSOC）的特別顧問<ref name="你所不知的生活的藝術">{{cite web |url=http://esango.un.org/irene/?page=viewProfile&type=ngo&nr=1291&section=9 |title=你所不知的生活的藝術 |publisher=Esango.un.org |accessdate=20 July 2010 |archive-date=2018-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181102103450/https://esango.un.org/irene/?page=viewProfile&type=ngo&nr=1291&section=9 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[古儒吉大師|古儒吉大師]]創立的另一個姊妹NGO組織為致力於抬升[[草根|草根]]層級人類價值的'''[[國際人性價值協會|國際人性價值協會]]'''（International Association for Human Values，縮寫'''IAHV'''）<ref name="國際人性價值協會">{{cite web| url= http://www.iahv.org/| title= 國際人性價值協會| publisher= Iahv.org| accessdate= 20 July 2010| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20100714061918/http://www.iahv.org/| archivedate= 2010年7月14日| deadurl= no}}</ref>。

==組織==
[[File:Art_of_Living_International_Ashram.JPG|thumb]]生活的藝術國際中心]]
AOLF的國際總部位在印度[[班加羅爾|班加羅爾]]的Ved Vignan MahaVidyaPeeth（縮寫VVM）校區（常被指稱為班加羅爾生活的藝術國際機構，或班加羅爾修道院，區域中心遍及150多個國家。在歐洲，該組織又名「內在成長協會」<ref>原題Association for Inner Growth</ref>。基金會係由[[古儒吉大師|古儒吉大師]]所創，在全球有各式各樣的個人發展及創傷舒緩計畫。

AOLF自1989年起始有美國的教育暨人道組織。1996年獲准為聯合國非政府組織，地位為聯合國ECOSOC的特別顧問，參與攸關健康、教育、永續發展、衝突解決及災難救援等議題的各式委員會及活動。<ref>{{cite web| url= http://www.un.org/esa/coordination/ngo/| title= 聯合國－經濟及社會事務部－非政府組織科| publisher= Un.org| accessdate= 18 March 2011| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110501104626/http://www.un.org/esa/coordination/ngo/| archivedate= 2011年5月1日| deadurl= no}}</ref>生活的藝術（以下簡稱'''AOL'''）為隸屬於'''新聞部'''（Department of Public Information，縮寫'''DPI'''）的NGO，在通訊及致力於達成聯合國目標（諸如「{{link-en|千禧年計劃|United Nations Millennium Campaign}}」及「消除貧窮」舉措）上扮演著活躍角色。

該組織大部分的官員及其多數的教師和職員都是義工。許多人道計畫、災難救援成就及訓練計畫都是透過或偕同姊妹組織IAHV執行的。<ref name=iahv_sch>{{cite news|title=坦米爾納德邦為海嘯受害孩童成立的學校開幕|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2007-07-21/india/27994115_1_tsunami-free-education-school-compound|accessdate=30 July 2013|newspaper=[[印度時報|印度時報]]|date=21 Jul 2007|archive-date=2014-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202124031/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2007-07-21/india/27994115_1_tsunami-free-education-school-compound|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。一些重要的各地分會有：生活的藝術基金會（美國）、Vyakti Vikas Kendra（印度）、Die Kunst des Lebens<ref>德文，「生活的藝術」之意</ref>（德國）、生活的藝術中心（加拿大）、南非生活的藝術、巴西生活的藝術及阿根廷生活的藝術。

該基金會積極以慈善組織的方式營運，開設基於瑜伽、呼吸及冥想等的AOL紓壓課程。
<ref>Gautier、Francois。《[http://www.books.com.tw/products/F011273363 喜悅的上師] {{Wayback|url=http://www.books.com.tw/products/F011273363 |date=20200418113835 }}》。紐約：Hay House，2008年。</ref>

AOL依[[古儒吉大師|古儒吉大師]]的和平哲學<ref>除非我們擁有一個沒有壓力的心智及無暴力的社會，我們是無法達成世界和平的。</ref>提供各種消除壓力及自我發展計畫，這些計畫主要是基於呼吸技巧、冥想及瑜伽。AOF的希望線（hopeline）計畫為一致力於減緩自殺傾向的24小時熱線，全年無休。<ref>{{cite web|title=希望計畫－青年賦權世界聯盟（原題''Project Hope - World Alliance for Youth Empowerment''）|accessdate=25 April 2011}}</ref>

該組織的提升生命/舒緩創傷之核心技巧（{{link-en|'''淨化呼吸法'''|Kriyā#Sudarshan Kriya}}，及其預備練習）已發表於許多[[同行評審|同行評審]]的國際期刊上。這些研究羅列其身心益處，包括減少壓力層級、增強免疫系統、舒緩焦慮及（輕中重度）憂鬱，<ref>{{cite journal | pmid = 10708840 | volume=57 | issue=1-3 | title=憂鬱症者練習「淨化呼吸法瑜伽」（Sudarshan Kriya Yoga）的抗抑鬱成效：隨機取樣[[電痙攣療法|電痙攣療法]]和{{le|丙咪嗪|Imipramine}}交相比較 | year=2000 | pages=255–9 | author = Janakiramaiah N; Gangadhar B.N; Naga Venkatesha Murthy P.J; Harish M.G; Subbakrishna D.K; Vedamurthachar A }}</ref>以及強化抗氧化保護力、提升腦功能（增加精神集中力、平靜感、從壓力刺激中平復）和其他發現。<ref>Gautier、Francois。《[http://www.books.com.tw/products/F011273363 喜悅的上師] {{Wayback|url=http://www.books.com.tw/products/F011273363 |date=20200418113835 }}》。紐約：Hay House，2008年。頁155-164。</ref><ref>AOL修練的科學研究 http://www.aolresearch.org/published_research.html {{Wayback|url=http://www.aolresearch.org/published_research.html |date=20210309172709 }}</ref>

雖非宗教組織，AOL卻透過各中心的社區服務延伸觸角，其計畫的參與人背景五花八門，來自不同的傳統和宗教，AOL的基本原則合乎[[不二論|不二論]]哲學。<ref>Melton, J. Gordon（2003）《[http://www.books.com.tw/products/F010179008 美國宗教百科] {{Wayback|url=http://www.books.com.tw/products/F010179008 |date=20200418111345 }}》（七版）。Farmington Hills，密西根：Gale publisher，頁1004。ISBN 0-7876-6384-0</ref>

2014年三月份，該組織位於[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]的[[伊斯蘭瑪巴德|伊斯蘭瑪巴德]]瑜伽中心被焚毀<ref>{{cite news|title=警方調查瑜伽中心是否因與印度及創始人古儒吉大師有關聯而被鎖定。|url=http://newsweekpakistan.com/art-of-living-center-torched-in-islamabad/|accessdate=25 June 2014|work=Newsweek|agency=Newsweek|publisher=AG Publications|date=2014-03-10|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126153837/https://www.newsweekpakistan.com/art-of-living-center-torched-in-islamabad/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=巴基斯坦的電視爭論是否促使瑜伽中心被焚？|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/did-pakistan-tv-debate-prompt-burning-yoga-center-n49036|accessdate=25 June 2014|publisher=NBC News|date=2014-03-10|archive-date=2021-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210405234044/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/did-pakistan-tv-debate-prompt-burning-yoga-center-n49036|dead-url=no}}</ref>，據聞是[[塔利班|塔利班]]的威嚇行動。<ref>{{cite web|title=塔利班威脅巴基斯坦的AOL義工|url=http://www.outlookindia.com/news/article/Taliban-Threatens-Art-of-Living-Volunteers-in-Pakistan-AOL/844058|publisher=Outlook|accessdate=25 June 2014|archive-date=2014-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141210141853/http://www.outlookindia.com/news/article/Taliban-Threatens-Art-of-Living-Volunteers-in-Pakistan-AOL/844058|dead-url=no}}</ref>

根據美國分會2006年七月到2007年六月份的報稅紀錄，AOLF的總歲入達美金550萬（主要的350萬來自課程費用，170萬來自捐助），而總支出為360萬。2007年七月初的淨資產計有770萬美元。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.guidestar.org/FinDocuments//2007/770/240/2007-770240101-03db3e53-9.pdf |title=愛荷華州費爾菲爾德AOLF－組織所得稅申報，IRS 2006 |format=PDF |accessdate=20 July 2010 |archive-date=2021-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123132851/http://www.guidestar.org/FinDocuments/2007/770/240/2007-770240101-03db3e53-9.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>AOLF美國分會的{{link-en|EIN|Employer Identification Number}}為77-0240101。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.guidestar.org/organizations/77-0240101/art-living-foundation.aspx |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-04-15 |archive-date=2013-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130518102122/http://www.guidestar.org/organizations/77-0240101/art-living-foundation.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==社會服務==
AOL投入全球許多社會服務，工作範圍涵蓋了化解衝突，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://portal.unesco.org/en/ev.php-URL_ID=3112&URL_DO=DO_TOPIC&URL_SECTION=201.html |title=聯合國教科文組織－衝突解決及「和平生活的藝術」 |publisher=Portal.unesco.org |accessdate=20 July 2010 |archive-date=2017-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171228225152/http://portal.unesco.org/en/ev.php-URL_ID%3D3112%26URL_DO%3DDO_TOPIC%26URL_SECTION%3D201.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>災難及創傷援助，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thaindian.com/newsportal/india-news/art-of-living-providing-trauma-relief-in-china_10056131.html |title=AOL在中國提供創傷援助 |publisher=Thaindian.com |date=3 June 2008 |accessdate=20 July 2010 |archive-date=2018-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181218151138/http://www.thaindian.com/newsportal/india-news/art-of-living-providing-trauma-relief-in-china_10056131.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thaindian.com/newsportal/india-news/art-of-living-trauma-relief-through-broadcast-in-china_10056012.html |title=AOL透過廣播在中國進行創傷援助 |publisher=Thaindian.com |date=3 June 2008 |accessdate=20 July 2010 |archive-date=2018-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181218145602/http://www.thaindian.com/newsportal/india-news/art-of-living-trauma-relief-through-broadcast-in-china_10056012.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>扶貧、婦女自強、受刑人更生、<ref name=SA_prison>{{cite news|title=南非囚犯擁瑜伽|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/7777912.stm|publisher=BBC News|date=24 December 2008|first=Andrew|last=Walker|accessdate=2015-04-17|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109033642/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/7777912.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>全民教育、反虐殺女嬰運動<ref>{{cite news|title=Nirmala對殺女嬰提出抗議|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2009-09-13/bangalore/28079205_1_female-foeticide-female-child-ratio-aol|work=[[印度時報|印度時報]]|date=13 Sep 2009|accessdate=2015-04-17|archive-date=2011-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110913095828/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2009-09-13/bangalore/28079205_1_female-foeticide-female-child-ratio-aol|dead-url=yes}}</ref>及童工和環境永續性等議題。<ref>{{cite news|title=SAIL的CSR施恩於農民|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2009-08-21/ranchi/28200321_1_icar-csr-drive-farmers|work=[[印度時報|印度時報]]|date=21 August 2009|accessdate=2015-04-17|archive-date=2014-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202124026/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2009-08-21/ranchi/28200321_1_icar-csr-drive-farmers|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="mge_100mil_pune">{{cite news|title=AOL抗全球暖化計畫|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2009-03-14/pune/28016135_1_global-warming-aol-seeds|work=[[印度時報|印度時報]]|date=14 Mar 2009|accessdate=2015-04-17|archive-date=2014-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202124029/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2009-03-14/pune/28016135_1_global-warming-aol-seeds|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2007年基金會發起了「{{link-en|Vidarbha|Vidarbha}}企劃－Swavalamban計畫」，旨在支援、訓練及鼓勵嚴重乾旱地區的農民返回生活常軌。除了AOL的課程之外，逾千名志工提供農民有機農法、零預算農耕、蒐集雨水、衛生、建造廁所等訓練。該計畫的成功獲得官方認可並持續在其他地區複製。<ref>{{cite news|title=AOL解救Vidarbha農夫|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/mumbai/1088337/report-art-of-living-rescues-vidarbha-farmers|newspaper=DNA|date=2 Apr 2007}}</ref>基金會在這項計畫上的總投注金額接近750萬[[印度盧比|盧比]]，州政府的金援達140萬盧比，協會大部分善款來自企業捐助，部分則是自費。<ref>{{cite web|title=貸款減免之後，無AOL課程給Vidarbha農夫|url=http://www.indianexpress.com/news/after-loan-waiver-no-art-of-living-course-for-vidarbha-farmers/327921/1|work=[[印度快報|印度快報]]|date=27 June 2008}}</ref>[[安得拉邦|安得拉邦]]亦有教育農民的類似創舉，其實施「零預算農耕」以終結自殺案例。<ref>{{cite news|title=古儒吉大師助AP農夫|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2008-01-07/hyderabad/27745935_1_zero-budget-farming-state-farmers-religious-conversions|work=[[印度時報|印度時報]]|accessdate=11 June 2013|date=7 January 2008|archive-date=2014-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202124038/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2008-01-07/hyderabad/27745935_1_zero-budget-farming-state-farmers-religious-conversions|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2008年發起的「起來行動吧！綠地球任務」運動則夥同{{link-en|聯合國千禧年計劃|United Nations Millennium Campaign}}及[[聯合國環境署|聯合國環境署]]在世界各地種植一億顆樹木以減緩全球暖化、保護環境。為支持聯合國的千禧年發展目標，AOL亦開始在印度境內植樹，作為綠地球運動的一部分。<ref name="mge_100mil_pune" /><ref>{{cite web|title=AOL發起「起來行動吧！綠地球任務」|url=http://news.oneindia.in/2008/10/04/art-of-living-launches-mission-green-earth-stand-up-take-action-1223114635.html|publisher=news.oneindia.in|accessdate=11 June 2013|archive-date=2014-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202173734/http://news.oneindia.in/2008/10/04/art-of-living-launches-mission-green-earth-stand-up-take-action-1223114635.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=學生響應「綠地球任務」|url=http://www.hindu.com/2008/10/04/stories/2008100450970200.htm|work=[[印度教徒報|印度教徒報]]|accessdate=11 June 2013|location=印度[[清奈|清奈]]|date=4 October 2008|archive-date=2008-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081008004823/http://www.hindu.com/2008/10/04/stories/2008100450970200.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref>而在2010年，[[孟加拉|孟加拉]]的基金會則參與了[[聯合國環境署|聯合國環境署]]主辦的「十億樹運動」。<ref>{{cite web|title=植十億樹|url=http://archive.thedailystar.net/newDesign/news-details.php?nid=162343|publisher=每日星報（原題''The Daily Star''）|accessdate=11 June 2013|archive-date=2014-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201205354/http://archive.thedailystar.net/newDesign/news-details.php?nid=162343|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=十億樹運動的新聞|url=http://www.plant-for-the-planet-billiontreecampaign.org/billiontreecampaign/CampaignNews/index.asp|publisher=[[聯合國環境署|聯合國環境署]]|accessdate=11 June 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130620205220/http://www.plant-for-the-planet-billiontreecampaign.org/billiontreecampaign/CampaignNews/index.asp|archivedate=2013年6月20日}}</ref>2013年二月份，「為印度的明天當義工」運動又有另一項為期三年的計畫，旨在偕同民間機構和環保分子復育班加羅爾的Kumudavathi河，透過蒐集雨水、增加植被、疏浚現有的[[梯井|梯井]]和其他方法來解決水資源短缺的問題。義工們和村民每週日在地理學家的指揮下參與這些活動。<ref name=TOI_Kumudvathi>{{cite news|title=AOL發起復育Kumudavathi河計畫|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2013-03-18/bangalore/37813379_1_river-basin-villages-water-scarcity|accessdate=23 June 2013|newspaper=[[印度時報|印度時報]]|date=18 March 2013|archive-date=2013-06-24|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130624234253/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2013-03-18/bangalore/37813379_1_river-basin-villages-water-scarcity|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=NIE_Kumudavathi_1>{{cite news|title=盼有更多水可用|url=http://newindianexpress.com/cities/bangalore/Hoping-for-more-water/2013/06/22/article1646640.ece|accessdate=23 June 2013|newspaper=新印度快報（原題''The New Indian Express''）|date=22 June 2013|archive-date=2014-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140823053131/http://www.newindianexpress.com/cities/bangalore/Hoping-for-more-water/2013/06/22/article1646640.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>為讓更多人認識這項計畫，AOL創辦人[[古儒吉大師|古儒吉大師]]率領其他NGO組織、社會碩彥、民間組織和眾多農夫、義工們在[[班加羅爾|班加羅爾]]市步行募款。<ref name=DNA_Kumudvathi_walkathon>{{cite news|title=Kumudvathi復育引發市民關注|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/bangalore/1845702/report-kumudvathi-revival-plan-draws-citizens-interest|accessdate=23 June 2013|newspaper=DNA報|date=9 June 2013|archive-date=2013-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130613032452/http://www.dnaindia.com/bangalore/1845702/report-kumudvathi-revival-plan-draws-citizens-interest|dead-url=no}}</ref>除了復育鳥獸所用的集水區，<ref>{{cite news|title=古儒吉大師領眾為水步行募款|url=http://www.business-standard.com/article/news-ians/ravi-shankar-leads-walkathon-for-water-113060800505_1.html|accessdate=23 June 2013|newspaper=Business Standard|date=8 June 2013|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120105429/https://www.business-standard.com/article/news-ians/ravi-shankar-leads-walkathon-for-water-113060800505_1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>迄2014年六月，該計畫已在七個村鎮內讓五個集水井恢復生機，同時設立了74個巨石哨點、疏濬了18座梯井並種植了2,350棵樹苗。<ref>{{cite news|title=他馴服了慣犯的犯罪本能|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/bangalore/He-tames-criminal-instincts-in-jailbirds/articleshow/36263869.cms|accessdate=25 June 2014|work=[[印度時報|印度時報]]|agency=TNN|publisher=[[印度時報|印度時報]]|date=Jun 9, 2014|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411004551/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/bangalore/He-tames-criminal-instincts-in-jailbirds/articleshow/36263869.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===為印度的明天當義工===
2012年十二月5日，AOL偕同聯合國機構、NGO及民間社會發起了「'''為印度的明天當義工'''」（暫譯，原文'''Volunteer For a Better India'''，縮寫'''VFABI'''）。VFABI涉入過許多活動，包括[[印度黑公交輪姦案|德里輪姦案]]的抗議行動。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-12-21/mumbai/35952963_1_vips-azad-maidan-silent-vigil | work=[[印度時報|印度時報]] | title=Mumbaikars發動人民守夜譴責德里暴行；尋求市民全體、而非只是VIP的安全－印度時報 | date=2013-05-10 | accessdate=2015-04-17 | archive-date=2013-09-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921061044/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-12-21/mumbai/35952963_1_vips-azad-maidan-silent-vigil | dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2013年五月，VFABI和{{link-en|印度醫學協會|Indian Medical Association}}共同設立了108個免費的健康站，計有1,634名志工在262名醫師的指揮下分發市值220萬盧比的藥品給兩萬多名德里的貧民窟居民。<ref>{{cite news|title=AOL為貧民窟居民設立免費健康站|url=http://www.business-standard.com/article/news-ians/free-health-camps-for-slum-dwellers-by-art-of-living-113051000649_1.html|accessdate=29 July 2013|newspaper=Business Standard|date=2013-05-10|archive-date=2020-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200420223801/https://www.business-standard.com/article/news-ians/free-health-camps-for-slum-dwellers-by-art-of-living-113051000649_1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年九月份的「為印度的明天投票」創舉激起了公眾對投票重要性的自覺，人們認知到這是他們對國家的責任。<ref>{{cite news|title=基金會督促公民去投票|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/pune/Foundation-urges-citizens-to-vote/articleshow/24172020.cms|accessdate=28 November 2013|newspaper=[[印度時報|印度時報]]|date=2013-10-15|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116094957/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/pune/Foundation-urges-citizens-to-vote/articleshow/24172020.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>如有五百多名義工負責[[浦那|浦那]]市的400多個住宅協會、60間公司及30所學院，收錄進名冊的投票人數達三萬五千多人。<ref>{{cite news|title=NGO義工編35,000人進投票人名冊|url=http://www.sakaaltimes.com/NewsDetails.aspx?NewsId=5179866745637335037&SectionId=5494605966908300850&SectionName=Civic&NewsDate=20131101&NewsTitle=NGO%20volunteers%20enrol%2035,000%20people%20in%20voters%E2%80%99%20list|accessdate=28 November 2013|newspaper=Sakal時報|date=2013-11-01|archive-date=2016-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161108235711/http://www.sakaaltimes.com/NewsDetails.aspx?NewsId=5179866745637335037&SectionId=5494605966908300850&SectionName=Civic&NewsDate=20131101&NewsTitle=NGO%20volunteers%20enrol%2035,000%20people%20in%20voters%E2%80%99%20list|dead-url=no}}</ref>而[[那格浦爾|那格浦爾]]{{link-en|沙旺工程學院|Yeshwantrao Chavan College of Engineering}}的學生在自己的學院也響應了此次行動，他們為自身、家人和朋友登記投票人身分卡。<ref>{{cite news|title=沙旺工程學院支持「為印度的明天投票」行動|url=http://www.nagpurtoday.in/ycce-supports-i-vote-for-better-india-campaign/|accessdate=28 November 2013|newspaper=那格浦爾今日報|date=2013-10-11|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124114156/https://www.nagpurtoday.in/ycce-supports-i-vote-for-better-india-campaign|dead-url=no}}</ref>

