AOL基於呼吸練習和冥想來籌劃課程。{{link-en|淨化呼吸法|Kriyā#Sudarshan Kriya}}是AOL課程的大部分主軸<ref name=toi_course_firemen>{{cite news|title=孟買消防員的Prāṇāyām課程|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2013-02-04/mumbai/36741994_1_fire-station-pranayam-sudarshan-kriya|accessdate=1 August 2013|newspaper=[[印度時報|印度時報]]|date=4 Feb 2013|archive-date=2013-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921122231/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2013-02-04/mumbai/36741994_1_fire-station-pranayam-sudarshan-kriya|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，部分課程的講師也都是義工。<ref name=usf_students>{{Cite web |url=http://www.usforacle.com/usf-community-learns-the-art-of-living-1.2814809#.UTR8oaDtGTY |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202204859/http://www.usforacle.com/usf-community-learns-the-art-of-living-1.2814809#.UTR8oaDtGTY |archive-date=2014-02-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>這些課程開設給學生、教職員、<ref name=usf_students />政府官員、<ref>{{cite news|title=30名州官員練習AOL消除壓力|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2003-06-14/mumbai/27173293_1_workshop-crime-branch-stress|accessdate=1 August 2013|newspaper=印度時報|date=14 Jun 2003|archive-date=2013-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921214749/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2003-06-14/mumbai/27173293_1_workshop-crime-branch-stress|dead-url=yes}}</ref>消防員、<ref name=toi_course_firemen />洗心革面的好戰分子、<ref>{{cite news|title=前叛軍領袖的冥想課程|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-03-12/guwahati/31152597_1_ulfa-vocational-training-militants|accessdate=1 August 2013|newspaper=印度時報|date=12 Mar 2012|archive-date=2013-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921134544/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-03-12/guwahati/31152597_1_ulfa-vocational-training-militants|dead-url=yes}}</ref>及囚犯等人上。<ref name=SA_prison />

